{"tid":371024,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Fate/Apocrypha 我屌你老母","createTime":"2017-08-23T11:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T13:16:58.000Z","uid":119080,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"035911e0a716260a6d89a1abfcb1d38109e4ba8c","tid":371024,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"成套野開始左8集 仲停留係英靈回憶同埋吹水劇情 <br />\n英靈打鬥下下停哂手 點到即止 <br />\n<br />\n好心睇下UFO套FATE UBW <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第0集打鬥已經打到飛天 爆哂劍氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://8maple.ru/110973/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F8maple.ru%2F110973%2F&d=JMzn%2FmBfnRP%2F7ql3QMWPqZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=56fd7ec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://8maple.ru/110973/</a><br />\nD劍氣仲要勁到 方圓300里既人都可以由肉眼見到<br />\n<br />\n屌你Fate/Apocrypha D打鬥 成個小學雞MODE咁<br />\n雙方派一推骷髏兵 人造人 兩邊都派D送死既廢角色出黎打冷場<br />\n屌你有幾可一套動漫會由小兵拎到英雄人頭???<br />\n好心有小小常識就咪派膠啦2邊既腦殘領袖<br />\n<br />\n呢幾集仲停留係D英靈出場秒殺小兵自Hi既場面<br />\n<br />\n英靈:我係XXX 既HERO阿 你把廢卒理所當然擋我唔住<br />\n<br />\nON99 我唔撚係要睇呢D打唔到肉到打鬥阿<br />\n<br />\n同我解放寶具真名互片 用爆哂令咒既生死對決阿唔該<br />\n<br />\n屌你齊格飛 第4集:幻想巨....劍  劍字都味叫出黎就神劇情死撚左<br />\n<br />\n人地5戰紅A 干將 莫邪同L叔 穿刺之死棘枪 隻抽 D火花同格劍聲 <br />\n鐵與鐵既碰撞聲真係好撚好J阿屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n垃圾Fate/Apocrypha快撚D打得精彩D阿唔該!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"c0541b665a62a560d1606f8f9e28674fb932cc83","tid":371024,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"輕小說改動畫你想有咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c4ff7ca8cd633d876b407f6ddce616f831a6a0","tid":371024,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"作者叫東出祐一郎,未聽過"},{"pid